{
  "id": "5c658a668da6c8001753ba87",
  "title": "愚かな一貫性は狭い心が生み出すお化け",
  "created": 1550158439,
  "updated": 1667411130,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c658a668da6c8001753ba87",
      "text": "愚かな一貫性は狭い心が生み出すお化け",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158439,
      "updated": 1550158439
    },
    {
      "id": "608faf42aff09e00000738e2",
      "text": "「[一貫性]が大事だ」という考えは、頭の悪い人が陥る誤った思考である、という考え方。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029251,
      "updated": 1620029251
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658a67aff09e000099d972",
      "text": ">A foolish [consistency] is the hobgoblin of little minds --- Ralph Waldo Emerson",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158439,
      "updated": 1550158596
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658a88aff09e000099d973",
      "text": "\t[Self-Reliance - Wikipedia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-Reliance]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158472,
      "updated": 1550158532
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658ac3aff09e000099d974",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158532,
      "updated": 1550158532
    },
    {
      "id": "608faf65aff09e00007aea76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029286,
      "updated": 1620029286
    },
    {
      "id": "608faf65aff09e00007aea77",
      "text": ">A foolish consistency is the hobgoblin of little minds, adored by little statesmen and philosophers and divines. With consistency a great soul has simply nothing to do. He may as well concern himself with his shadow on the wall. Speak what you think now in hard words, and to-morrow speak what to-morrow thinks in hard words again, though it contradict every thing you said to-day. — 'Ah, so you shall be sure to be misunderstood.' — Is it so bad, then, to be misunderstood? Pythagoras was misunderstood, and Socrates, and Jesus, and Luther, and Copernicus, and Galileo, and Newton, and every pure and wise spirit that ever took flesh. To be great is to be misunderstood.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029286,
      "updated": 1620029287
    },
    {
      "id": "608faf67aff09e00007aea78",
      "text": ">[Ralph Waldo Emerson], Self Reliance (1841)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029287,
      "updated": 1620029287
    },
    {
      "id": "6362acb7aff09e00003807c3",
      "text": "\t愚かな一貫性は、小さな政治家、哲学者、神学者に慕われる、小さな心のホブゴブリンである。偉大な魂は、一貫性とは無縁なのだ。壁に映る自分の影を気にしているのと同じことかもしれない。今思っていることを厳しい言葉で話し、明日、明日思っていることを厳しい言葉で話しなさい、たとえそれが今日あなたが言ったこととすべて矛盾していても。- ああ、だからあなたは必ず誤解されるのだ」 「では、誤解されることはそんなに悪いことだろうか？ピタゴラスも、ソクラテスも、イエスも、ルターも、コペルニクスも、ガリレオも、ニュートンも、これまでに肉体を得たすべての純粋で賢明な精神も誤解されたのだ。偉大であることは、誤解されることである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667411128,
      "updated": 1667411130
    },
    {
      "id": "6362acb7aff09e00003807c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667411128,
      "updated": 1667411128
    },
    {
      "id": "6362acb7aff09e00003807c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667411128,
      "updated": 1667411128
    },
    {
      "id": "608faf67aff09e00007aea79",
      "text": "[偉大であることは、誤解されること] >To be great is to be misunderstood.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029287,
      "updated": 1620029843
    },
    {
      "id": "608fb17daff09e00000738ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1620029821,
      "updated": 1620029821
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658b06aff09e00005a80f8",
      "text": "[愚かな一貫性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158598,
      "updated": 1550158603
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658b0baff09e00005a80fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158603,
      "updated": 1620029249
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658b0eaff09e00005a80fc",
      "text": "関連: [奴隷道徳]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158606,
      "updated": 1550158667
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658b47aff09e00005a80fd",
      "text": "\t「一貫性は善である」という思考を盲信するのは奴隷道徳",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158663,
      "updated": 1550158736
    },
    {
      "id": "5c658b6daff09e00005a8100",
      "text": "\t一貫性は有用か？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550158701,
      "updated": 1550158743
    },
    {
